Ponyta

Evolves At 5

Pastel Veil

Passive Ability

The Pokémon's psychic counter charges based on the distance they run (up to 10 times). When the counter is full, the Pokémon is granted a shield, becoming hindrance resistant while the shield remains.

When the Pokémon reaches an additional movement speed threshold, the damage dealt by moves is increased by 5/20/35/50/60%. Fairy Wind's damage is instead increased by 5/43/115/135/150% per additional movement speed threshold. The increased damage based on movement speed is calculated before dealing damage with moves.

Please visit the FAQ to learn more!

89.6% SpA + 0 x (Level - 1) + 224

Attack

Auto Attack

Shoots energy from their horn, damaging the opposing Pokémon hit.

67.5% SpA + 0 x (Level - 1) + 90

Confusion

Move 1

4.00s Area

The user releases a telekinetic force around themself, increasing their movement speed by 33% per opposing Pokémon hit for 5.5s (up to 2 times; maximum 66%) before damaging opposing Pokémon in the area of effect when it hits.

100% SpA + 8 x (Level - 1) + 350

Confusion Upgrade Choices

Dazzling Gleam

4.50s Area

The user emits a powerful flash around themself after a delay, damaging opposing Pokémon in the area of effect when it hits. The user gains 1 stack of 11% increased movement speed per wild Pokémon hit by the outer edge of the flash, or 2 stacks per Pokémon from the opposing team hit for 5.5s (up to 9 stacks; maximum 99% increased movement speed) before damaging them. If the outer edge of the flash hits Pokémon from the opposing team, the cooldown of Tackle, Smart Strike, or Agility is reduced by 30% of its current cooldown, successively with each target hit.

Against wild Pokémon: Dazzling Gleam damage is capped at 2500.

153% SpA + 15 x (Level - 1) + 215

Strengthens the cooldown reduction of Smart Strike or Agility to 50% of its current cooldown successively per Pokémon from the opposing team hit by the outer edge.

Fairy Wind

7.00s Area

The user jumps to the designated location then stirs up a fairy wind when they land, damaging opposing Pokémon in the area of effect. This move can be used again, up to 2 times total.

If it's used 2 times, the third attack deals increased damage and throws opposing Pokémon for 0.8s when it hits.

71.5% SpA + 9 x (Level - 1) + 100

117.7% SpA + 15 x (Level - 1) + 179

Decreases the movement speed of opposing Pokémon hit by 20% for 2s with each use.

Tackle

Move 2

7.00s Sure Hit

The user charges at the designated opposing Pokémon, damaging them and decreasing their movement speed by 20% for 2s when it hits.

100% SpA + 8 x (Level - 1) + 250

Tackle Upgrade Choices

Smart Strike

9.00s Sure Hit

The user charges at the designated opposing Pokémon and stabs them with their sharp horn, dealing damage when it hits. The user then leaps in a chosen direction, shoving the target in the opposite direction and stunning them for 1s.

97% SpA + 8 x (Level - 1) + 155

Charges the user's psychic counter by 5 when this move hits.

Agility

2.00s Buff

The user's movement speed increases by 5% when this move is used, increasing by an additional 7.5% every 0.5s over 3s (maximum 80% increased movement speed).

This move's duration increases by 1.5s if the user moves or hits opposing Pokémon with moves (up to 5 times for an additional 7.5s; maximum 10.5s duration).

Also restores 2% of the user's missing HP every 0.5s while their movement speed is increased by this move.

Triad Blitz

Unite Move

112s 100000 Sure Hit

Unlocks at level 9

The user becomes unstoppable and charges at the designated opposing Pokémon, shoving opposing Pokémon in the way and stunning them for 0.8s when hit. When the charge ends, a mysterious triangular space is created around the designated opposing Pokémon if the user hits them. That Pokémon cannot leave that space.

When the mysterious space is created, this move can be used again up to 3 times within 5.5s. With each additional use, the user runs at high speed forward, damaging opposing Pokémon in their path. If the path of a dash starts or ends in the mysterious space, this move can be used again immediately afterward. Otherwise, there is a 3s cooldown between dashes.

100% SpA + 8 x (Level - 1) + 200

Unite Buffs (6s duration):

30% Movement Speed, 30% CDR, 20% Max HP Shield
